> A simple strongly-typed pub/sub/fire eventing system

## Installation

```shell
npm install --save subscribableevent
```

## Basic Example

```typescript
const event = new SubscribableEvent<(payload: string) => void>();

event.subscribe((payload: string) => {
    console.log(payload);
});

event.fire('Payload Params');
```

